project_descr: Projet Fonds Mondial de lutte contre le VIH le Paludisme et la Tuberculose round 5 en République Démocratique du Congo.

outputs.output_descr: The Program aims to reduce mortality and morbidity due to the TB and due to TB-HIV co-infection in the Congolese population by increasing the treatment success rate to 85 and the rate of case detection to 75 % of expected tuberculosis cases.
donor_name: GLOBAL FUND TO FIGHT AIDS, TUBERCULOSIS
